1 A SENATE RESOLUTION CONFIRMING EDDIE M. BUFFALOE, JR., AS SECRETARY
2 OF THE DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.
3 Be it resolved by the Senate:
4 SECTION 1. Having given due consideration to the matter, the Senate confirms
5 Eddie M. Buffaloe, Jr., as Secretary of the Department of Public Safety.
6 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
